high_descs: Turn and go to the bathtub.
Pick up a candle on the bathtub.
Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Put the candle on the counter by the sink.
Turn and go to the cabinet under the sink.
Take a candle out of the cabinet under the sink.
Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Put the candle on the counter by the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles to the counter by the sink.

high_descs: Head to the corner of the sink in front of the shower.
Pick up the candle off the top of the sink.
Turn around and go to the middle of the storage cabinet to the left side of the toilet.
Place the candle in front of the purple rag on top of the table.
Head to the the left end of the table.
Open the cabinet on the bottom of table and take out another candle.
Head back to the middle of the table.
Place the candle beside the other one in front of the purple rag on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place two candles on the middle of the storage table.

high_descs: Walk over to the foot of the tub.
Pick up the candle from the edge of the tub.
Walk over to the counter in between the two sinks.
Put the candle down on the counter in front of the rag.
Walk over to the sink on the left side and look below the sink at the cabinet.
Open the cabinet, take the candle out of the cabinet, and close the door.
Walk to the counter in between the two sinks.
Put the candle down on the counter to the right of the first candle.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles to the counter in between the sinks.
